subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: Venus Williams, the top seed and defending champion, was upset in the opening round of the WTA’s Cellular South Cup in Memphis by Petra Kvitova, a 17-year-old qualifier. Kvitova won the fifth WTA Tour match of her career, stunning Williams, the winner of four Wimbledon titles, 2-6, 6-4, 6-3.
